Citation.sTitle: Excess Molar Volumes and Surface Tensions of Xylene with 2-propanol or 2-methyl-2-propanol at 298.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: Densities for binary mixtures of (2-propanol + o-xylene, + m-xylene, + p-xylene, 2-methyl-2-propanol + o-xylene, + m-xylene, + p-xylene) have been determined at 298.15 K and excess molar volumes have been derived. Surface tension of these binary mixtures have been measured at 298.15 K by the pendant drop method and the values of the surface tension deviation for these mixtures were also calculated.
